node.text: Nothing beats a clean shave, except for maybe a QUEER shave! As we move into the final moments of #pridemonth, I’m partnering with @harrys, who is donating 💯 percent of the proceeds from their Shave with Pride collection (including this cute iridescent razor) to the @trevorproject, the world’s largest suicide prevention and crisis intervention organization for LGBTQ youth. Head to harrys.com to shop! 🏳️‍⚧️🏳️‍🌈💛💜 #harryspartner #shavewithpride #ad

node.text: Sharing the stage with this man is a giggle factory ! Our annual pride ride is always in celebration of queer culture and history, and im always honored to hold this space for the @onepeloton community. Thank y’all for showing up and being part of this years celebration 🏳️‍⚧️🏳️‍🌈🤎🖤💜💛 @djjohnmichael
